cv.title: FULLSTACK DEVELOPER
cv.description: I am currently studying to become a fullstack developer. I have a lot to learn, and I'm really looking forward to working life. Something I know will be fantastic thanks to my amazing teachers and students!

cv.title: ORGANIZATIONAL PSYCHOLOGY
cv.description: I studied individuals' work-related experiences, reactions and actions in relation to the content and organization of work and how to interact with groups and organizations. I also learned a lot about how to implement change in a positive way!

cv.title: CHIEF OPERATING OFFICER
cv.description: I ran a transport company, doing everything from lifting pianos to making the website. I say yes to everything, like to focus on details but can also look up and see the big picture. I am convinced that a prosperous organization begins with the well-being of the staff, so they were always my main focus.

cv.title: FALL PROTECTION ASSEMBLER
cv.description: I installed fall protection at high alitudes. With rope, harness and helmet, I've been able to see the most beautiful views of Gothenburg. It's pretty surreal to work hanging in a harness 25 floors up!
